<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="405" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="12.[1409,2616,884,1430]" pageId="12" pageNumber="405">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1411,1763,1317,1350]" pageId="12" pageNumber="405">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Distribution, abundance, and population trend of the Kashmir Shrew are unknown.
